{"tid":2072193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"暴動罪成「佔旺女村長」獄中撼頭自殘　邵家臻：因被職員打罵已作投訴","createTime":"2020-06-20T12:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T14:41:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0c282101f0e599c6ad4b8de9feef881dd995b518","tid":2072193,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E4%BD%94%E6%97%BA%E5%A5%B3%E6%9D%91%E9%95%B7-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E6%92%BC%E9%A0%AD%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%98-%E9%82%B5%E5%AE%B6%E8%87%BB-%E5%9B%A0%E8%A2%AB%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%89%93%E7%BD%B5%E5%B7%B2%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E6%2597%25BA%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%259D%2591%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E7%258D%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2592%25BC%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%2598-%25E9%2582%25B5%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%2587%25BB-%25E5%259B%25A0%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=86d3bd2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E6%2597%25BA%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%259D%2591%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E7%258D%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2592%25BC%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%2598-%25E9%2582%25B5%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%2587%25BB-%25E5%259B%25A0%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&h=104919f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E4%BD%94%E6%97%BA%E5%A5%B3%E6%9D%91%E9%95%B7-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E6%92%BC%E9%A0%AD%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%98-%E9%82%B5%E5%AE%B6%E8%87%BB-%E5%9B%A0%E8%A2%AB%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%89%93%E7%BD%B5%E5%B7%B2%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4/</a><br />\n<br />\n羅湖懲教所人員上周發現，一名 24 歲暴動罪成的女囚犯，在院所醫院觀察室内突然情緒不穩，並以頭撞向閘門及地下，懲教人員立即喝止並召喚支援到場，她被轉送到公立醫院作進一步診治。社福界立法會議員邵家臻今（20 日）在 FB 證實該女囚犯為 2016 旺角騷亂案、暴動罪成判囚的「佔旺女村長」畢慧芬，稱她因被職員打罵而情緒激動自殘，邵家臻指她清楚說出職員姓名，已作投訴。"},{"pid":"3bb610445542214c00cb733a8eeb782477641d54","tid":2072193,"uid":282352,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"肯定懲教狗打的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32873a31e37c2ebea64bdfbbc67dbf415c8e461","tid":2072193,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/posts/1403247433194570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbottleshiukachun%2Fposts%2F1403247433194570&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=aab539f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bottleshiukachun/posts/1403247433194570</a><br />\n<br />\n邵家臻<br />\n9 hrs &middot; <br />\n星期五，先去荔枝角收押所再去小欖精神病治療中心再回立法會開會投票，￼舟車勞頓，都有點累￼：<br />\n<br />\n1，酷熱天氣之下，監房地份外酷熱，一般比場外的世界高兩至三度，坐監的人都說天上有九個太陽。酷熱之下，皮膚病會爆發，有濕疹有汗癬，手足都又痕又腫，食不下咽，夜不能眠。￼￼但礙於之前是買成藥，或者已經失去醫生證明，所以外邊的藥膏不能hand in。院所內的藥膏多數無料到，這些日子，痕得辛苦￼。<br />\n<br />\n2，法庭重開，又時煩惱的時候，手足面對審訊，要認還是不認？認，有三份一刑期減免；不認，就要博一舖，真是人生交叉點。手足要考慮的因素很多，其中會考慮其他手足的反應和評語。苦苦掙扎，流出眼淚來。我只能呼籲牆外的手足一定要尊重牆內的手足的決定，抗爭的日子長的呢￼。<br />\n<br />\n3，雖然我想經常公務探訪，申請時是要先得手足同意，署方才准許我前行，但到院所的一刻，手足仍可因為各種原因拒絕探訪。今次有個手足拒絕接受我探訪（俗稱彈鐘），￼雖然是一記悶棍，我都十分尊重。畢竟人在囚室，百感交集￼￼，選擇留白，是可以理解的。￼<br />\n<br />\n4，從懲教署新聞公告知道一名羅湖女懲教所的犯人有自殘行為，所以被送往醫院￼￼。查實是女村長Amy。￼￼他說因為被職員打罵，情緒激動，￼以致撼頭埋牆￼。既然女村長說得清楚，￼有名有姓，已作投訴。<br />\n<br />\n5，手足之所以是手足，多是路見不平，有手足為外籍囚友爭取打IDD的權利；為跨性別囚友爭取權利，叫人感動。"},{"pid":"4441cd114d172b44c9e4af33d43e6b6a42192da6","tid":2072193,"uid":322044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93430c61014446ee87ab35e26f957c44707b7f1","tid":2072193,"uid":44209,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"女村長好慘<br />\n佔旺嗰單今年先判，而且仲背負住機場嗰單&rdquo;暴動&rdquo;，真係有機會坐十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdeb01e63d1e955d20fb83348c86059ddef34a8","tid":2072193,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf51d2aa3b960e5aae685c43d4279e543384f67","tid":2072193,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"一早講抗爭者剩係識坐監唔work."},{"pid":"7c0b855b7b0a46428f9a54ec4057e0f47a175f68","tid":2072193,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbf51d2aa3b960e5aae685c43d4279e543384f67","tid":2072193,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"一早講抗爭者剩係識坐監唔work."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"唔係可以點啊"},{"pid":"691434f55ceee7421f081e9c0cb326dbd5d7cd62","tid":2072193,"uid":11830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fbf51d2aa3b960e5aae685c43d4279e543384f67","tid":2072193,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"一早講抗爭者剩係識坐監唔work."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"你條撚樣死撚咗佢啦 講到有人想坐監咁<br />\n係度扮智者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1260fad8f1f70c171c8c38f82694c379d06ad55e","tid":2072193,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:13:09.000Z","msg":"邵家臻有冇幫佢爭取雞翼大隻D<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/ZGHMw7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FZGHMw7.png&h=81fb1178&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce48ac73c11cf900bf8dfe60d8ba060718fc8df8","tid":2072193,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e93430c61014446ee87ab35e26f957c44707b7f1","tid":2072193,"uid":44209,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"女村長好慘<br />\n佔旺嗰單今年先判，而且仲背負住機場嗰單&rdquo;暴動&rdquo;，真係有機會坐十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:13:09.000Z","msg":"更正返，原來係上年11月判"},{"pid":"03eb6a20065db56429ae16ea04b88e45f919846b","tid":2072193,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c0b855b7b0a46428f9a54ec4057e0f47a175f68","tid":2072193,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbf51d2aa3b960e5aae685c43d4279e543384f67","tid":2072193,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"一早講抗爭者剩係識坐監唔work."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"唔係可以點啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"自焚都得,<br />\n總之就唔好殺人啦."},{"pid":"bc9a32ff62ec5d9f7a42071cde13f7a204aab231","tid":2072193,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"剛剛庭上見到佢<br />\n精神問題好似好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好勇武 係法庭大叫光時五缺黑口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aedb9b5cd0d4a78d85809e95b3afb2a296d172e","tid":2072193,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc9a32ff62ec5d9f7a42071cde13f7a204aab231","tid":2072193,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"剛剛